- Betrayal was
the only thing that felt

00:24.190 --> 00:27.079
real to me.
I trusted you.

00:27.120 --> 00:30.578
- Let me help you.
- I need your help.

00:30.630 --> 00:33.428
- (Jack): We investigated
your claims about Dr. Lecter.

00:33.460 --> 00:37.328
We found nothing. You stood
over Cassie Boyle's body
in that field and

00:37.370 --> 00:41.158
you described yourself to me.
- (Will): No, I described
Hannibal Lecter.

00:41.200 --> 00:44.169
- (Beverly): You
think Will is innocent.
- I don't know what I think.

00:44.210 --> 00:47.236
- I think he still wants to save
lives. That's what I think.

01:19.580 --> 01:22.105
(electricity buzzing)

01:43.300 --> 01:45.518
(electricity buzzing)

01:57.680 --> 01:59.648
- (man): Mr. Graham, it's time.

