thought of as super-villains.

06:23.050 --> 06:26.474
- And what was
your first Impressmn?
- He was intelligent.

06:26.520 --> 06:27.873
And arrogant.

06:27.920 --> 06:31.048
And very likely
on the spectrum.

06:31.090 --> 06:35.550
- Which is why he wasn't
real FBI. He didn't pass

06:35.590 --> 06:38.889
