08:40.050 --> 08:43.645
We have to create desire
to find you "not gthy,"

08:43.690 --> 08:46.284
_ which is nonexistent
In this courtroom right now.

08:46.320 --> 08:49.289
We're manipulating people
into buying something
they don't need.

08:49.320 --> 08:52.118
- Mr. Brauer?
- They don't want
your innocence. Thank you.

08:52.160 --> 08:54.151
_ Unconsciousness
in a pretty package,

08:54.200 --> 08:56.191
