listened to her.

16:12.370 --> 16:14.634
- Do you blame yourself
for her death?

16:18.640 --> 16:20.631
- I blame Will Graham.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.038
- Thank you.

16:27.080 --> 16:28.479
Your witness.

16:32.490 --> 16:34.082
- Miss Lounds.

16:36.090 --> 16:38.285
